Text: This story is never untold to anyone. This is the chance to let many people
  know what many people feel when their heart tpuched by love from The Greatest. Many
  people have connected to other but many of them can not have real relationship.
  This story let us learn how to understand what your partner feel what ever they
  do. Let your heart set free with love to everyone that you meet. This story makes
  you know that God always works in our life.
